window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>It was just another sunny day at the coast when a life was changed forever...</b></p> <p>What started as a prank for a young girl resulted in the elevation of a crab's existence. Now, wrenched from its happy life at the beach, the crab...HAS AWAKENED.</p> <p>Sir Crabby finds himself thrust into sapience. Into a world filled with creatures both mundane and magical, a world where evil lurks beneath the waves.</p> <p>Join Sir Crabby as he travels beneath the ocean, discovering power, adventuring forth and searching for his young friend as he's thrust into the Eternal Conflict of Arthos.</p> <p><b>Bestseller Ryan Rimmel, author of </b><b><i>Noobtown</i></b><b>, teams up with Boe Hagen to bring you this hilarious and unique LitRPG Series about the most unlikely of heroes who gains access to a System, and all the wacky adventures that ensue.</b></p>"; 
